OL,4,CFord says farewell to 'Mondeo man' as
OL,5,Ccar to be phased out
OL,6, A car that became the byword for a
OL,7, certain type of British motorist will
OL,8, finally be put out to pasture next year
OL,9, after 29 years in production.
OL,11,FThe Ford Mondeo was launched in the UK
OL,12,Fin 1993 and has sold five million since
OL,13,Fon the back of popularity with both
OL,14,Ffamilies and executives.
OL,16,FBut demand has shifted towards SUVs and
OL,17,Flower-emission cars.
OL,19,FSo production of the Mondeo will stop
OL,20,Fat Ford's Valencia plant in early 2022,
OL,21,Fthe company said.
